---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |DISTRIBUTED INSERT                    |               |1       |35          |
|1 |└─PX COORDINATOR                      |               |1       |22          |
|2 |  └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR                |:EX10001       |1       |22          |
|3 |    └─SUBPLAN SCAN                    |ANONYMOUS_VIEW1|1       |20          |
|4 |      └─MERGE JOIN                    |               |1       |20          |
|5 |        ├─EXCHANGE IN MERGE SORT DISTR|               |1       |12          |
|6 |        │ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (PKEY) |:EX10000       |1       |11          |
|7 |        │   └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR   |               |1       |11          |
|8 |        │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN       |t2             |1       |11          |
|9 |        └─SORT                        |               |1       |9           |
|10|          └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR     |               |1       |9           |
|11|            └─TABLE FULL SCAN         |t1             |1       |9           |
=================================================================================
